We're talking to John
Brandenburg and Monica Rix

00:10:33.650 --> 00:10:37.080 align:middle line:84%
Paxson about this very,
very interesting book--

00:10:37.080 --> 00:10:38.390 align:middle line:90%
it reads like a novel--

00:10:38.390 --> 00:10:40.850 align:middle line:90%
called "Dead Mars, Dying Earth".

